dc_description_s: This feature class contains line features representing evacuation routes in the City of Philadelphia. Evacuation routes have been designated for Pedestrians and Mass Transit Only, Pedestrians and All Vehicles, Private Vehicles Only, and Pedestrians Only. This feature class was compiled as part of the City of Philadelphia's evacuation planning process beginning in 2007. Data is updated bi-monthly based on changes to the City's street centerline file. Feature Update Date: 12-2012
